:309781,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點證明自己信？</blockquote><br />\n有人問過即刻扮信教入去見識下得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n答案係no<br />\n我地想去要信教起碼1年<br />\nKeep住去佢地個信仰的活動<br />\n你個長老保你就可以入麥加了<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去果啲崇拜活動係做乜？有乜得着？</blockquote><br />\n每個宗教都有聖地<br />\n等於耶撚既耶路撒冷，共匪既井岡山<br />\n冇咩得著純粹去左會high d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶路撒冷 有冇禁止 非耶撚入?<br />\n<br />\n井岡山 有冇禁上 非中共黨員入??"},{"pid":"dd911e6bf7e897f7eecf11a8db6366b70a21c202","tid":309781,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜原來個光頭佬好呢味野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔爭氣</blockquote><br />\n我都笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/195852_8b46c4e784b7c92abdccd00cdbe001fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F195852_8b46c4e784b7c92abdccd00cdbe001fb.jpg&h=ef64ef66&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇到張圖先明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沫原來唔係穆試林唔呵以入來曖度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67500c15d8a72b3411eaf197cba9d3307844dd2","tid":309781,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"從來未見過左膠批評呢d名乎其實既宗教歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390af03fedebaad140e3cf525c66a04c80d6889a","tid":309781,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"[wow]"},{"pid":"6f8ff05c12d143790f43d945d7ec9f89aa237c06","tid":30